Dudley Moore Character Information

Gender: Male ♂ Status: Deceased Occupation: Actor Relatives: Wife: Susan Anton First appearance: "Bart Has Two Mommies"

Dudley Moore was an English actor.

History[edit]

When Maude looked down onto the Earth, Bob Hope said that he had not seen such climbing since Dudley Moore got married to Susan Anton.

Appearances[edit]

Episode – "Bart Has Two Mommies" (mentioned)
